---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - onticket">
  <Navbar lang="en" />
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none text-gray-600">
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: December 16, 2025</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        At <strong>onticket</strong>, your privacy is our priority. This policy explains how we handle your information when you use our mobile application and our website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>To provide you with the expense tracking service, we need to process the following data:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email and password (encrypted) for secure authentication via Firebase Auth.</li>
        <li><strong>Expense Data:</strong> Titles, amounts, dates, categories, and images (receipts) that you voluntarily upload.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Basic device information for error management and performance.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>We use your information exclusively to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Provide the app functionality (save and view your expenses).</li>
        <li>Sync data between your devices in the cloud.</li>
        <li>Improve user experience and fix bugs.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>We DO NOT sell or share your personal data with third parties for advertising purposes.</strong></p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        Your data is stored securely on <strong>Google Firebase</strong> servers. We use encrypted connections (SSL/TLS) for all communications between your device and the server.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Access your data.</li>
        <li>Rectify incorrect data.</li>
        <li>Delete your account and all your data directly from the app (Settings > Delete Account).</li>
        <li>Export your data in standard formats (CSV/Excel).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this policy, you can contact us at: <a href="mailto:analyticszone@onmedic.org" class="text-primary hover:underline">analyticszone@onmedic.org</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
